## Review Scope

{{ review_scope | default("full") }}

**Named scopes** (defaults to `full` if not specified):

- `full` -- evaluate all eight dimensions (FD1-FD8).
- `adapter_pr` -- focus on FD1 (Layering) + FD2 (A-rules) + FD3 (Security) + FD6 (Tests/conformance) + FD7 (Anti-Patterns). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend-explainability/lib/adapters/`.
- `ui_component_pr` -- focus on FD2 (U-rules) + FD3 (Security) + FD4 (Accessibility) + FD5 (Performance) + FD7 (Anti-Patterns). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend-explainability/components/` or `frontend-explainability/app/`.
- `wire_translator_pr` -- focus on FD2 (W-rules + T-rules) + FD6 (wire schema drift). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend-explainability/lib/wire/` or `frontend-explainability/lib/translators/`.
- `security_audit` -- FD3 + FD7 only.
- `sprint_audit` -- FD8 only. Use for sprint-board re-derivation runs.

